    "description": "<p>You <strong>summon</strong> apparitions of weapons on the field, then take a defensive stance as you @EFFECT[guard]. Each apparition can be destroyed in either of two ways: It can be attacked directly or you can use a suitable <strong>Objective</strong> action in order to clear a <strong>3-section hard clock</strong>.</p><p>At the <strong>end of the round</strong> you deal damage to all your enemies. <strong>For each</strong> apparition still present when the round ends, you deal an <strong>additional</strong> instance of damage, up to a <strong>minimum of 1</strong> for all weapons destroyed.</p><ul><li><p><strong>You</strong>: @LOSS[20 mp]</p></li><li><p><strong>Targets</strong>: @DMG[$minor untyped]</p></li></ul><p></p>",
